  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.3.1">
<l>ūṉil vāḻuyirē nallai pōvuṉṉaippeṟṟu</l>
<l>vāṉuḷār perumāṉ matucūta ṉeṉṉammāṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṉum yāṉu mellān taṉṉuḷḷē kalantoḻintōn</l>
<l>tēṉum pālu neyyuṅ kaṉṉalu mamutumottē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Living in the flesh, life, you are good. Go! Obtaining you,</l>
<l>the great man of those who are in heaven, Madhusūdana, our lord</l>
<l>himself and I, we remain mingled inside all,</l>
<l>similar to honey, milk, ghee and sugarcane.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
